snippet.title: Sonic 3D Blast in TRUE 3D (N64)
snippet.description: After a long while, the next bonus stage in Sonic Mushroom Blast is finished after weeks of photoshopping and faithfully recreating Green Grove from Sonic 3D Blast for my SM64 Sonic Mod.
